  "text": "• Fresh Aggregates: For each entity (or query) that occurs in a sufficiently large number of contexts, we get the set of users who have that entity (query) in any of their contexts. We then aggregate what those users have read recently. [CITATION_1] Thus for a given entity, we have aggregate statistics on what fresh content would be interesting for users with that entity.",
